{"id": "aos027", "name": "Audio_Noah_702_08_03", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, be careful.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Sister, I'm fine... You don't have to hold on to me.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "You just got discharged. Let your sister help you out, just in case.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "He has a point. Here, give me your hand.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Oh... okay.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "The fans are all worried about you. Look at all these letters and gifts.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "I saw them.\nSince I already arrived home, I need to report my status to everyone on iM.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, I'm coming in?\nHow are you doing? Do you feel any discomfort?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "I'm doing fine... My head doesn't hurt anymore.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Time right now: 21:00. Medicine time! Medicine time!</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Ah, I'll go prepare it for you. You like your water hot but not too hot, right?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... Sister, when we were little... where did we live?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Eh? Quadrant II 02 street... What's the matter? Did you remember something?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... Is it Node 03?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... No, it's Node 08.\nIf we have the time, I should take you back for a visit. However, right now, you should rest some more. Don't overthink yourself.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Have I ever been to Node 03 before then?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Eh? Let me think... When you're around fourteen, we did have plans to go there during one of Noah's long breaks... However, the travel agency told us that it's quite dangerous there, so we ended up not going.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Is that so...</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Ah, nothing...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... You should stop thinking about these first. You need to let your brain rest. I'll go get your medicine.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_6", "Singing"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "*そろそろ試合終了の鐘を鳴らしてよレフェリー\nいつの間に 氷も溺れたアイスティー*\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Why are you practicing singing again? Noah told you that you need to rest for now...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "It's okay... I'm just humming it casually.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, you like singing way too much. How troublesome...\nHere, take your medicine. Once you're done with that, you can go to bed early.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "What song was that? It was great.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Has sister not heard this before?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Yep. Even though I know nothing about singing, I remember every single one of your songs clearly, including those that are still just DEMOs.\nThat melody you were just humming feels really nice. Is it Aroma's own creation?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "I don't know... It's probably...... I think? The words just come out themselves without me realizing.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "It really is a great song. A very fresh style too.\nIt's getting late. We should record it tomorrow. I'll let the composers have a listen.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">It somehow feels like...</font>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Hmm?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... Nothing. I... I really like this song.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma、気を付けて。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "お姉ちゃん、大丈夫だから……\n支えてくれなくても平気。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "やっと退院できたんだ。\n心配だから、支えてもらった方がいいよ。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ほら、言ったじゃない。手、貸して。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "うん……分かった。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ファンの子たちもみんなとても心配してるわ。\nほら、メッセージもプレゼントもこんなにたくさん。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "うん。\niMでみんなに無事だって報告しなくちゃいけないね。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma、入るわよ？\n大丈夫？具合悪くない？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "大丈夫……もう頭痛もしない。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>21時デス！薬の時間！薬の時間！</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あら、持ってきてあげるわ。\nお湯は熱すぎない方がいいのよね。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……お姉ちゃん、私たち……昔はどこに住んでたの？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "え？第三象限の02通りよ……どうして？\n何か思い出した？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……それって、Node03？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……違うわ。Node08よ。\n今度連れて行ってあげるわね。\nでもしばらくは身体を休めることに集中して。\n余計なことは考えちゃダメ。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "じゃあ……私、昔Node03に行ったことある？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "え？そうね……\nあなたが14歳くらいの頃に、Noahが長期休暇を取れるからって行こうとしてたけど……\n旅行会社の人にあそこは危険だって言われて、結局やめたの。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">そっか……</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "あ、なんでもない……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……とりあえず、考えないようにして、頭を休ませるのよ。\n薬取ってくるわね。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_6", "歌声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "*そろそろ試合終了の鐘を鳴らしてよレフェリー\nいつの間に 氷も溺れたアイスティー*\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "どうして歌の練習なんかしてるの？\nNoahがしばらくはゆっくり休みなさいって言わなかった？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "大丈夫……口ずさんでるだけだから。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "もう、Aromaは本当に歌が好きね……\nほら、薬。早く飲んで、早く寝なさい。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "さっきのなんて曲？いい曲ね。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "お姉ちゃん聞いたことないの？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ないわ。\nお姉ちゃん、歌のことは分からないけれど、あなたの歌なら全部脳に刻まれてるわ。\nまだ作ってないデモの分もよ。\nさっきの曲のメロディよかったわよ。\nAromaが作ったの？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "分からない……たぶん……？\n無意識に口ずさんでたの。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "本当にいい曲だったわよ。\nスタイルも新鮮でいいし。\n今日はもう遅いから、明日録音しましょう。\n編曲の先生に聴かせるの。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">思うんだけど……</font>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ん？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……ううん……私、この曲好き。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，小心走。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "姊姊，我沒事……不用扶沒關係。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好不容易才出院，保險起見，讓姊姊扶吧。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "就是說啊，來，手給我。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……好。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "粉絲們都很擔心呢，妳看，收到這麼多信跟禮物。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯，已經到家了，得用 iM 跟大家報個平安才行。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，我進來囉？\n還好嗎？有沒有哪裡不舒服？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "還好……頭已經不會痛了。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>現在時間：21：00，吃藥時間！吃藥時間！</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，我去幫妳準備，水不要太燙對吧？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……姊姊，我們小時候……住在哪裡啊？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "咦？第三象限 02 街呀……怎麼了？是不是想起什麼了？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……Node 03 嗎？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……不，Node 08。\n有空應該帶妳回去看看的，不過最近還是先多休息吧，別想太多。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "那我以前有去過 Node 03 嗎？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "咦？我想想……大概妳十四歲的時候，有一次 Noah 放長假我們有打算去那邊玩玩……但旅行社說那邊蠻亂的，最後還是沒去。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">是嗎……</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "啊，沒事……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……先別試著想這些了，讓頭腦休息一下吧，我去幫妳拿藥。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_6", "歌聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "*そろそろ試合終了の鐘を鳴らしてよレフェリー\nいつの間に 氷も溺れたアイスティー*\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "怎麼又開始練唱了呢？Noah 說了這段期間要好好休養的……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "沒關係的……只是隨口哼哼。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "傷腦筋，Aroma 實在太喜歡唱歌了……\n來，吃藥囉，吃了趕快睡吧。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "剛才那是什麼歌啊？很好聽耶。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "姊姊沒聽過嗎？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "嗯，我雖然不懂唱歌，不過妳的歌我可是全都記在腦海裡，包含還沒做的 DEMO 也是。\n剛剛那段旋律感覺很不錯呢。是 Aroma 的創作嗎？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "我不知道……好像是……吧？不知不覺就唱起來了。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "真的很好聽，風格也很新鮮。\n很晚了，明天有空錄下來吧，我拿給編曲老師聽看看。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">總覺得……</font>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……沒有，我……很喜歡這首歌。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, 조심!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "언니, 난 괜찮아... 부축해주지 않아도 돼.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "이제 막 퇴원했잖아. \n그래도 당분간은 도움을 받는 게 좋을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "들었지? 자, 팔 내밀어 봐.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응... 알았어.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "팬들도 많이 걱정하고 있어. 자, 이것 봐. 네게 보내온 팬레터와 선물들이야. 엄청 많지?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응. 집에 도착했으니 iM으로 모두에게 걱정하지 말라고 말해야겠어.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, 들어갈게.\n좀 괜찮아? 어디 불편한 곳은 없고?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "괜찮아... 두통도 사라졌어.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "<i>지금 시각: 21：00, 약 먹을 시간! 약 먹을 시간!</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "아, 내가 할게. 물은 너무 뜨겁지 않게, 맞지?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "...언니... 우리 어렸을 때... 어디에 살았어?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응? 제3사분면 02 길목에 살았잖아... 왜 그러니? 뭔가 기억이라도 돌아온 거야?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "...Node 03 구역이었어?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "아니, 우리는 Node 08에서 살았어.\n시간 날 때 한 번 데리고 갈 테니깐 지금은 우선 쉬는 일에만 신경 쓰자.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "그럼... 내가 Node 03에 가본 적은 있어?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응? 어디 보자... 네가 14살 때 Noah가 장기 휴가를 받아서 놀러 가려고 한 적이 한 번 있었는데... 여행사에서 위험하다고 하길래 결국은 안 갔어.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">그랬구나...</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "아, 아니야...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...우선 생각하려 하지 말고  머리 좀 쉬게 해 줘. 나는 가서 약 좀 가져올게.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "고마워.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_6", "노랫소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "*そろそろ試合終了の鐘を鳴らしてよレフェリー\nいつの間に 氷も溺れたアイスティー*\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "또 그런다 또? Noah도 지금은 안정을 취하는데 집중하라고 했었잖...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "괜찮아... 그냥 흥얼거리는 정도인데 뭘.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "정말 이럴 땐 골치 아프다니깐. 새삼스럽지만 Aroma는 진짜로 노래하는 것을 좋아하는구나... 약 먹어. 어서 먹고 눈 좀 붙이도록 해.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "고마워.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "방금은 무슨 곡이야? 엄청 좋다.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "언니는 안 들어봤어?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응. 내가 노래에 대해 잘 아는 것은 아니지만, 그래도 네가 불렀던 노래들은 아직 DEMO로 나오지 않은 곡까지 전부 기억하고 있거든. 방금 그 멜로디 꽤 괜찮던데, Aroma가 직접 만든 거야?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "모르겠어... 아마도 그런 거 아닐....까? 나도 모르게 그냥 입에서 흘러나왔어.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "스타일도 뭔가 참신하고 참 좋은 곡 같아. \n지금은 늦었으니깐 내일 시간 날 때 녹음해서 편곡 선생님한테 들려줘 보자.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">내 생각에는……</font>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "아, 아니야... 이, 이 노래 너무 좋다고....\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs":